(9, 'Ranjit Kumar', 'ranjit@yahoo.com', 'Ranjit Kumar is a senior advocate practising in Supreme Court of India and the present Solicitor General of India. He was appointed in 2014 by the incumbent government of Narendra Modi, succeeding Mohan Parasaran', 2147483647, '15000', 1, '2017-07-14 15:40:10', '2017-07-14 15:40:10'),
